<chapter line="1">Kathāvatthu-aṭṭhakathā</chapter>
<gatha1 line="2">Nisinno <pageBreak edition="P" number="0.0001" /><pageBreak edition="M" number="0.0105" /><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0100" />devalokasmiṃ, devasaṅghapurakkhato;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="3">Sadevakassa lokassa, satthā appaṭipuggalo.</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="4">Sabbapaññattikusalo, paññattiparidīpanaṃ;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="5">Vatvā puggalapaññattiṃ, loke uttamapuggalo.</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="6">Yaṃ puggalakathādīnaṃ, kathānaṃ vatthubhāvato;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="7">Kathāvatthuppakaraṇaṃ, saṅkhepena adesayī.</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="8">Mātikāṭhapaneneva <pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0101" />, ṭhapitassa surālaye;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="9">Tassa moggaliputtena, vibhattassa mahītale.</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="10">Idāni yasmā sampatto, atthasaṃvaṇṇanākkamo;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="11">Tasmā naṃ vaṇṇayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</gathalast>
